election_record.label: Ohio 1814 Governor

overview.note: The official certified totals were Thomas Worthington with 15879 votes and Othniel Looker with 6171 votes.

sub_unit.name: Adams
sub_unit.note: The Ohio Republican (Dayton, OH), The Miami Intelligencer (Hamilton, OH) and the Muskingum Messenger (Zanesville, OH) list Thomas Worthington with 626 votes.
The Western American (Williamsburg, OH) lists Thomas Worthington with 727 votes.

sub_unit.name: Butler
sub_unit.note: The Miami Intelligencer (Hamilton, OH) and the Spirit of the West (Cincinnati, OH) list Thomas Worthington with 523 votes.

sub_unit.name: Clermont
sub_unit.note: The Western Star (Lebanon, OH) and The Miami Intelligencer (Hamilton, OH) list Othniel Looker with 615 votes.

sub_unit.name: Clinton
sub_unit.note: The official certified vote lists Thomas Worthington with 134 votes and Othniel Looker with 5 votes.

sub_unit.name: Cuyahoga
sub_unit.note: No returns have been found for Cuyahoga County.

sub_unit.name: Fairfield
sub_unit.note: The Ohio Express lists Thomas Worthington with 945 votes, though the township totals add up to 925.

sub_unit.name: Gallia
sub_unit.note: The Spirit of the West (Cincinnati, OH) lists Othniel Looker with 50 votes.

sub_unit.name: Hamilton
sub_unit.note: The Western Spy (Cincinnati, OH) lists Thomas Worthington with 606 votes.

sub_unit.name: Muskingum
sub_unit.note: The Muskingum Messenger (Zanesville, OH), The Miami Intelligencer (Hamilton, OH), the Western American (Williamsburg, OH) and Ohio Republican (Dayton, OH) list Thomas Worthington with 823 votes.
The Zanesville Express, and Republican Standard (Zanesville, OH) lists William Craig with 50 votes.

sub_unit.name: Falls
sub_unit.note: The Zanesville Express, and Republican Standard (Zanesville, OH) lists Thomas Worthington with 105 votes.

sub_unit.name: Zanesville
sub_unit.note: The Zanesville Express, and Republican Standard (Zanesville, OH) lists Thomas Worthington with 220 votes.

sub_unit.name: Scioto
sub_unit.note: The Miami Intelligencer (Hamilton, OH) lists Othniel Looker with 317 votes.

sub_unit.name: Washington
sub_unit.note: The Ohio Republican (Dayton, OH) lists Thomas Worthington with 624 votes.
